# =============================================================================
# DATABASE & STORAGE NOTES (v0.9.0)
# =============================================================================

# hopeshot_news.db is intentionally excluded from version control because:
# - Contains user-specific article data and API responses
# - Database schema is recreated via database_setup.py script
# - Development databases should not be shared between team members
# - Production databases require separate deployment and backup strategies
#
# Configuration files (prompts.yaml, sources.yaml) are tracked to enable:
# - Collaborative prompt development and source management
# - Version history of experimental configurations
# - Shared A/B testing experiments across team members
# - Systematic tracking of prompt performance improvements
#
# Database structure is defined in code (database_setup.py) rather than
# committed database files for proper version control and team collaboration

# =============================================================================
# DUAL STORAGE ARCHITECTURE NOTES
# =============================================================================

# SQLite database files excluded but schema tracked in:
# - database_setup.py (initial schema creation)
# - database_migration.py (schema evolution scripts)
# - services/database_service.py (auto-creation logic)
#
# Google Sheets integration configured via:
# - .env file (GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID)
# - gsheetapi_credentials.json (excluded service account)
# - services/sheets_service.py (schema mapping)